  "Description": {
    "English": "Contained negative matter and baryogenesis antiparticles.<br> <br>The vast energy potential of antimatter makes it highly valuable. 95% of existing antimatter consumption is in the powering of <span class=\"name name-technology\">starship hyperdrives</span>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">WARNING</span>: uncontained usage is not recommended.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "其中包含负物质和重子反粒子。<br> <br>反物质的巨大能量潜力使它具有很高价值。95%的现有反物质用于为<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船超光速推进器</span>提供动力。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不推荐无节制的使用。",
    "TencentChinese": "其中包含负物质和重子反粒子。<br> <br>反物质的巨大能量潜力使它具有很高价值。95%的现有反物质用于为<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船超光速推进器</span>提供动力。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不推荐无节制的使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以容器裝載的負物質與重子生成反粒子。<br> <br>反物質可能蘊含強大能量，因此極為珍貴。目前的反物質總消耗量中，有 95% 是用來為<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船超空間驅動器</span>提供能量。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不建議暴露於外部使用。"
  },
