  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Antimatter from <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Condensed Carbon</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">Chromatic Metal</span>. Use <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> to craft in empty <span class=\"name name-technology\">Inventory Slots</span>.<br>Refine <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Condensed Carbon</span> from regular, plant-based carbon. Refine <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Chromatic Metal</span> from large mineral deposits found with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">浓缩碳</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>制作反物质。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">库存栏位</span>中制作。<br>使用普通植物碳精炼出<span class=\"name name-fuel\">浓缩碳</span>。使用通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>发现的大型矿床中的矿物精炼<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金属</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">浓缩碳</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>制作反物质。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">库存栏位</span>中制作。<br>使用普通植物碳精炼出<span class=\"name name-fuel\">浓缩碳</span>。使用通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>发现的大型矿床中的矿物精炼<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金属</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">濃縮碳</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>製作反物質。用 <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> 在空的<span class=\"name name-technology\">道具欄位</span>製作。<br>一般常見的植物碳可精製成<span class=\"name name-fuel\">濃縮碳</span>。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>發現的大型礦物資源產地可精製出<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金屬</span>。"
  },
